     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr\" lang=\"fr\"><hr/><p><b>French</b></p><hr/><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CarteDeConcepts FRSectionImagingActLMCDAFHIR</b></p><a name=\"FRSectionImagingActLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><a name=\"hcFRSectionImagingActLMCDAFHIR\"> </a><p>This mapping does not specify any particular context of use.</p><br/><p><b>Groupe 1 </b>Mapping de <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-lm-acte-imagerie</code> to <code>https://interop.esante.gouv.fr/ig/document/core/StructureDefinition/fr-cda-dicom-acte-imagerie</code></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Code source</b></td><td><b>relation</b></td><td><b>Code cible</b></td></tr><tr><td>FRLMActeImagerie</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMActeImagerie</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMActeImagerie.codeSection</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMActeImagerie.code</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMActeImagerie.titreSection</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMActeImagerie.title</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMActeImagerie.blocNarratif</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMActeImagerie.text</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMActeImagerie.sousSection.complicationsActe</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equivalent\">is equivalent to</a></td><td>FRCDADICOMActeImagerie.component:frDICOMComplications</td></tr><tr><td>FRLMActeImagerie.sousSection.expositionsRadiations</td><td><a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R5/codesystem-concept-map-relationship.html#equivalent\" title=\"equiva